Dorothy Arnold (actress) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dorothy_Arnold_(actress) 0 Dorothy Arnold (November 21, 1917 – November 13, 1984) was an American film actress and the first wife of baseball star Joe DiMaggio. Her 20-year movie career began with 1937’s Freshies and ended with 1957’s Lizzie.
